content.description:
These cliffs stretch from the edge of the golf course and the Main Face along the island to where the cliff folds in on itself and there are several large tree covered ledges.  

  Exposed to midday to afternoon sun, the rock is vertical and typical Kineo style in terms of sharp geometric blocks, hard to protect, and prone to falling.  

  Secluded and seldom climbed, this section of the cliff contains the famous ice climb "Maineline (sp?"
